xc:entity.dcterms:title: Eastman School of Music Trombone Alumni Concert
xc:entity.dcterms:tableOfContents: O sacred head now wounded / J. S. Bach ; arr. Howard Hanson (6:20) (Neill Humfeld, conductor) -- Largo / Warren Benson (13:48) -- Achieved is the glorius work / Joseph Haydn ; arr. Don Miller (3:45) -- Adoramus te Christe / Quirino Gasparini ; arr. Don Miller (2:30) -- Adagio / Camille St. Saëns ; arr. Ken Murley (5:19) -- Sonara for trombone choir and percussion (World premiere) / Sal Scarpa (7:25) -- Passacaglia in c minor / J. S. Bach ; arr. Don Hunsberger (7:07) (Donald Hunsberger, conductor) -- I'm getting sentimental over you / Ned Washington ; arr. Rob Boone (4:47) (Tom Ervin, soloist) -- Wolf eyes / Paul Winter ; arr. Mark Lusk (4:19) (Mark Lust, soloist) -- Sweet Georgia Brown / arr. Steve Mortenson (6:29) (Bionic Bones with Jim Pugh, soloist ; Bill Dobbins, piano ; Bill Campbell, bass ; Rich Thompson, drums) -- Stardust for the chief / Rayburn Wright (6:10) (John Beck, drums, Alec Brinkman, bass ; Donald Hunsberger, conductor).
